{"tid":951650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那買咗咁多大豆係咪傻仔咗？","createTime":"2018-12-22T13:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T01:23:34.000Z","uid":195944,"like":259,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"79f5cdcec8cde124d08e8d9367ddfd72006c7f9b","tid":951650,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:38:57.000Z","msg":"大豆其中一個用途就係做豬糧<br />\n<br />\n但係咁啱得咁橋 支那又有非洲豬瘟爆緊 <br />\n<br />\n咁啲大豆俾邊個食？？<br />\n<br />\n吖 唔記得咗 支那仲有十四億人形豬 終於唔駛食草喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf7c5612208040dc216decb6d95b1ec0e7fca13d","tid":951650,"uid":195944,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:42:41.000Z","msg":"2018年肆虐全國多個省份的非洲豬瘟，最終在18日「殺入」廣東，佛山市順德區一個豬場出現疫情。但與廣東相鄰的湖南省，10月底就被豬瘟「攻陷」。《香港01》記者到湖南省益陽市桃江縣的發病豬場「志成豬場」直擊，當地10月40多隻豬發病，當局撲殺豬場全部500多隻活豬，以及方圓三公里範圍內所有豬場的活豬。<br />\n<br />\n因為非洲豬瘟，志成豬場在當地「聲名狼藉」。負責人向記者展示埋下500多隻豬的大坑，稱當時非常慘，即使在12月7日豬場已解封，豬場仍要被禁止養豬半年，來年生計仍無着落。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e017c14169339bc039637dd16b97cbe28f3b5169","tid":951650,"uid":107364,"like":11,"dislike":94,"score":-83,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:43:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3243ee7295fc9fb56a75ccc13c0f466ac2807567","tid":951650,"uid":4917,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:46:59.000Z","msg":"全民食豆腐"},{"pid":"bf6c009a307b34fe0fd53a217c9610c7e6f92d9e","tid":951650,"uid":195944,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:55:10.000Z","msg":"其實大豆仲有咩用途？ 點解美帝會揀大豆？"},{"pid":"1535fffe5f2e9eaa37676f81e28d079934a88b5e","ti